# ⭐ Advantages of Auto Configuration

* Reduces Boilerplate Code
* Faster Development
* Easy Configuration
* Production Ready
* Less XML
* Smart Defaults

---

# ❌ Limitations

* Higher Memory Usage
* Less Control
* Sometimes Difficult to Debug
* Unwanted Configurations May Load

